json.cardslot_explain:
1. Rule description:
There are 22 groups of player card slots, the first 11 groups are in the open state, and the last 11 groups are in the closed state; each group of card slots has 5 card slots, and cards can be combined freely;
The current 11 sets of cards are placed, and after submitting the combination, you can start to purchase the next 11 sets of card slots in sequence, the prices are respectively 10USDT, 20USDT, 30USDT...110USDT;
When submitting a combination, you must choose a mining farm to place cards and provide computing power;
2. Calculation of computing power:
1) Basic computing power:
The basic computing power of 2-K is 10 times the number of points (for example, the computing power of 2 is 20, and the computing power of J is 110);
The basic computing power of A is 150;
The king’s basic computing power is 100, and each card slot can only hold 1 king;
2) Combination bonus:
Pair bonus: 30%, flush pair bonus 60%;
Triple bonus: 60%, triple flush bonus 100%;
Bomb bonus: 120%, flush bomb bonus 200%;
Straight bonus: 150%, straight flush bonus 300%;
Black Joker bonus: 100%, Red Joker bonus 200%;

json.mine_explain:
1. Game introduction: 
 Each round of the mining pool lasts for 5 days. Starting from the 0th round, the activity time is the even-numbered round and the odd-numbered round is the rest time; the activity time is divided into 3 stages: stack day, Limited purchase day, and subscription day;
2. Activity time introduction 
1), Stack day (1-3 days)
Stake a certain number of PK coins (the name of the mine must be set before the first purchase), and obtain the number of card slot groups that can be restricted according to the percentage of the user’s total investment; (for example: this round of stack is 1000 PK, total stack is 5000 PK, is 20%, the total number of card slots released in this round is 3000, and the total number of card slots available for purchase restriction day is 3000*20%=600);
The stacked PK cannot be taken out during the purchase day, and can be taken out at any other time, and it can be received in the income panel;
2), Limited purchase day (the 4th day)
According to the user's stack ratio on the stack day, the user can purchase the corresponding number of card slot groups. (If there is no stack on the purchase day, Limited purchase and free purchases cannot be carried out)
3), Subscription day
Total number of card slots-quantity purchased on the limited purchase day = remaining quantity. Users can purchase the remaining card slot groups at will. (If there is no stack on the stack day, limlted purchase and free purchases cannot be carried out) 
3. Income  There are two parts of income: electricity fee income and service fee income;   1), electricity bill income For users who stacked in your mining farm, when receiving income, 20% USDT of the consumed electricity fee will be your electricity fee income;   2), service fee income Users who stacked in your mining farm, you will receive 5% PK of their income as your service fee income;

json.reward_explain:
1. The player enters the game by scanning your QR code, and buying a blind box once, will become your invitee;

2. To increase the number of invitation rewards, the following requirements must be met:

i. You have already purchased the blind box;

ii. The invitee enters the game through your QR code and purchases a blind box;

You are not the other party’s invitee;

json.energy_explain:
1. Electricity consumption

The calculation formula for power consumption: 1000 computing power consumption 1USDT under 28800 blocks;

2. Income

After the user signs up the card and submits the combination successfully, he gets a certain amount of computing power; in the current block, your computing power accounts for the total computing power of the entire network, that is, the proportion of your income in this block (for example, if Your computing power is 1000, the total computing power of the entire network is 10,000, and the current block reward is 1PK, then your income for the current block is 1000/10000*1PK=0.1PK);

When your electricity bill is sufficient, you can receive 95% of the income in full, and 5% will be paid to the mine as a service fee;

When your electricity bill is insufficient, you can only receive part of the income; it depends on your computing power value under each block;

json.nft_explain:
1. There are both Red Joker and Black Joker in the backpack, you can activate an NFT with special value in the activation panel;

2. There is only one chance to activate each card;

3. The activated NFT displays the words ‘Looking forward’, which means that the NFT has not been announced yet, once it is announced, it will be displayed automatically;

4. The three newly obtained NFTs will be displayed in the scene. In the details, all the obtained NFTs will be displayed;
